          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The first  measurement  of the 2H(g-pol,n)p analyzing",
                " power near threshold has been  performed  using  the",
                " High-Intensity Gamma-ray  Source  (HIGS) at the Duke",
                " Free-Electron Laser Laboratory.  A  3.58  MeV  g-ray",
                " beam having an energy resolution of 2.5 %  and 100 %",
                " linear polarization  was  incident  on   an   active",
                " liquid scintillating  (C-6)(D-12)  target.  Outgoing",
                " neutrons were detected parallel and perpendicular to",
                " the plane of g-ray polarization at a  lab  angle  of",
                " 150 degree.  The experimentally determined analyzing",
                " power provide a sensitive  measurement  of  the  the",
                " relative  E1 and M1 contributions to the total cross",
                " section."
              ]
            }
          ],
